<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
            font-optical-sizing: auto;
            background-color: #8a5a44;
            color: rgba(211,190,173,255);
        }
        @keyframes emerge {
            from {opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);}
            to {opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
        }
        .animated {
            animation: emerge 2s ease-out;
        }
        .title, .description, .image-container {
            visibility: hidden;
        }
        .title.animated {
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
        }
        .description.animated {
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }
        .image-container.animated {
            animation-delay: 3.5s;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(233,210,191,255);
        }
        p{
          font-size: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .description {
            max-width: 50%;
            color: rgba(233,210,191,255);
        }
        .image-container {
            width: 400px;
            height: 300px; /* Adjust as needed */
            
        }
        .image-container img {
              width: 400px;
              height: 100%;
              object-fit: contain; /* This will ensure the full image is shown */
              display: block; /* Removes the bottom margin/gap */
          }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="title animated">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
</div>
<div class="content">
    <div class="description animated">
        <p>Welcome to Global Ed-Hub, where your journey to finding the perfect college begins. In a world brimming with educational opportunities, making the right choice can be daunting. That's where we step in—Global Ed-Hub is your premier destination for personalized college recommendations, driven by cutting-edge technology and a deep understanding of the global educational landscape.</p>
          <p>
          Our Mission
          At Global Ed-Hub, we are committed to simplifying the college selection process for students worldwide. We understand that choosing a college is a decision that shapes your future. Thus, our mission is to empower students with comprehensive, AI-driven insights into colleges that align with their academic preferences, budget, and lifestyle choices.
        </p>
        <p>
          How We Do It
          Leveraging the latest in artificial intelligence and data analysis, Global Ed-Hub offers a unique platform where students can input their preferences—ranging from preferred courses and majors to budget constraints and desired living conditions. Our proprietary algorithm then processes this data to provide a curated list of colleges that match the student's criteria, complete with detailed recommendations to guide their decision-making process.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our Vision
          We envision a world where every student has access to the information and tools needed to make informed decisions about their education. Global Ed-Hub aims to be at the forefront of educational consultancy, bridging the gap between students and their ideal academic institutions across the globe.
        </p>
        <p>
          Why Choose Us?
          Personalized Recommendations: Tailored suggestions based on your individual preferences and requirements.
          Global Reach: Access to a wide array of colleges and universities from around the world.
          Simplicity and Accessibility: An easy-to-use interface and process that demystifies college selection.
          Data-Driven Insights: Our recommendations are backed by thorough research and cutting-edge AI technology.
          Join Us on Your Journey
          Whether you're just beginning to explore your college options or you're ready to make a decision, Global Ed-Hub is here to support you every step of the way. Explore our platform to discover how we can help you navigate your path to academic and personal growth.
          
          </p>


          <h1>"Empowering Your Educational Journey"</h1>
          <h1>- Bhavani K & Tazveen Zanab </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container animated">
        <!-- Replace with your image -->
        <img src="jj.png" alt="About Us Image">
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    // Simple script to add visibility to elements after animation starts
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
        const elements = document.querySelectorAll('.animated');
        elements.forEach(function(element) {
            setTimeout(() => {
                element.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }, 100); // slightly delay to sync with CSS animation
        });
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>
